Knowing your income and expenses, you can easily calculate how much you can afford to spend. Thus, it is very simple to get the actual cost value in just a couple of days of accounting, without waiting for the end of the month.

If you are just thinking where to start accounting for finances – the Pocket accounting application may be a good option: it requires minimal time and effort!
